'''Trygve Bruvik''' (born 1952) is a [[Norway|Norwegian]] [[engineer]] and [[businessperson]].

Bruvik was educated with an engineering degree from [[Bergen University College|Bergen College of Engineering]], as well as a business administration degree from [[BI Norwegian Business School]]. He worked for [[Vesta Forsikring]] from 1981, and was [[chief executive officer]] from 1994 to 2002. Since 2003 he has been chair of [[Marine Farms]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.marinefarms.com/content/view/73/42/ |title=Board of directors |author=[[Marine Farms]] |accessdate=2008-11-01}}</ref>

